<item>
            <title>[MSHADE-23] ${basedir} is wrong after running shade plugin</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MSHADE-23</link>
                <project id="12317921" key="MSHADE">Maven Shade Plugin (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After the shade plugin has run, the ${basedir} points to target.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
